l"},"usefulItems":"bowl, 4 serving bowls","hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook <\/em>or <em>Everyday Cookbook <\/em><em><\/em>for the Chicken stock paste recipe.","This is a very spicy Thai soup. For a truly authentic soup, use 6 chillies, but prepare for the heat!"],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","45m","4 portions"]}